íŸ@f7a838ff42a63dbf15cf4406145e1100e89b4ed95be466265e0e22192751364a⁄◊Title: title: str substring
Path: Examples
Content:
Get a substring "nushell" from the text "good nushell" using a range.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
>  'good nushell' | str substring 5..11
nushell

```
Count indexes and split using grapheme clusters.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
>  'üáØüáµ„Åª„Åí „Åµ„Åå „Å¥„Çà' | str substring --grapheme-clusters 4..5
„Åµ„Åå

```
sub string by negative index.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
>  'good nushell' | str substring 5..-2
nushel

```
